@startuml
title Statechart diagram of the plane lifecycle

[*] --> Order

state Order as "Order"
state Arrival as "Arrival"
state Preparation as "Preparation"
state Operations as "Operations"
state Maintenance as "Maintenance"
state OutOfService as "OutOfService"

Order --> Arrival : plane acquired
Arrival --> Preparation : arrived
Preparation --> Operations : prepared and scheduled flights exist
Operations --> Maintenance : no more scheduled flights or maintenance required
Maintenance --> Preparation : checked and serviced

Operations --> [*] : plane out of service permanently
Maintenance --> [*] : plane out of service permanently
OutOfService --> [*] : plane restored to service

@enduml
